evidence.source_document: Order Granting Plaintiffs' Motion for a Temporary Restraining Order
evidence.text: No monitor was appointed in this case. The court issued a temporary restraining order and preliminary injunction regarding the camping ordinance, but no monitoring requirements or reports were referenced in any document. The case does not involve a settlement requiring compliance monitoring.

Case involves temporary restraining order and preliminary injunction regarding San Rafael's camping ordinance (SMC 19.50), with no mention of court-appointed monitor in any document. The case focuses on constitutional challenges to the ordinance itself, not compliance monitoring.
